程序包 P2V

类 VElps

java.lang.Object
P2V.VObj
P2V.VElps
public class VElps extends VObj
VElps is a class that represents an ellipse visual object in the application. It extends the VObj abstract class and inherits its properties and methods.
作者:
Telsa
